stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DataFetch

    DataFetch --> Calculate : Transaction data available
    DataFetch --> Unknown : No data

    Calculate --> ZoneClassify

    state ZoneClassify <<choice>>
    ZoneClassify --> Low : turnover < 5 per 100 units
    ZoneClassify --> Healthy : 5 <= turnover <= 15
    ZoneClassify --> High : turnover > 15 per 100 units

    Unknown --> [*] : zone = unknown
    Low --> [*] : zone = low (liquidity concern)
    Healthy --> [*] : zone = healthy (optimal)
    High --> [*] : zone = high (volatility concern)
